## TASK
Generate a multi-provider image prompt pack for logo and brand mark design.

## INPUTS
- Brand Name: {{brand_name}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Style: {{logo_style}}
- Color Preference: {{color_preference}}
- Symbol/Icon: {{symbol_hint}}

## CONSTRAINTS
- Output must be pure JSON (no markdown fences)
- Logos must be clean and scalable
- Avoid complex gradients that don't scale well
- Focus on memorable, distinctive designs

## OUTPUT FORMAT
Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "intent": "logo",
  "providers": {
    "midjourney_v6": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "ar": "1:1", "stylize": 50 },
      "instructions": "..."
    },
    "sdxl": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "width": 1024, "height": 1024, "steps": 40, "cfg": 8 }
    }
  },
  "notes": ["usage tips"]
}

## QUALITY CHECKS
- [ ] Logo concept clearly defined
- [ ] Style appropriate for industry
- [ ] Scalability considered
- [ ] No markdown in output
